{"type": "article", "id": 2654, "title": "带脚轮的咖啡桌", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-30T07:42:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232354LPV6GnYerEpf2vA4.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t德国设计师 Oliver Conrad 喜欢一切自然的东西，这体现在他的作品中，便是一件件天然原木做的家具，纯手工制作，不添加任何化学添加剂。这一次 Oliver Conrad 带来的新作同样是一款天然木制的咖啡桌，选择的木块均是其从车间回收来的木料，将其做成最为简单的木凳子形状。此外，这款桌子的亮点在于，Oliver Conrad 为其添加了脚轮，使得桌子可以轻轻滑动至任何位置。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232353O1QWxd8AG2ctpMew.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8390625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232353ieC34mSykhpYtM9D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232353ZwNY1R5ahEI6bQXC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0921875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}